# UI Preview — Mandatory Gate After Every Component/Region

**Firma:** HorosCode · **Produkt:** HorosCloud

> **Never proceed to the next component or region until Preview is running and confirmed.**

## Rule

After implementing **any** component or region:

1. Create isolated `*Preview.axaml`
2. Run Preview (Viewer or `dotnet run` on preview project)
3. Verify visual output matches intent
4. **STOP** — show Preview to user (`12-human-approval`) before continuing

## File Pattern

```text
Views/Previews/HeaderPreview.axaml
Views/Previews/HeaderPreview.axaml.cs
ViewModels/Previews/HeaderPreviewViewModel.cs
```

## HeaderPreview Example

```xml
<Window xmlns="https://github.com/avaloniaui"
        xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
        xmlns:components="using:HorosCloud.Desktop.Views.Components"
        xmlns:vm="using:HorosCloud.Desktop.ViewModels.Previews"
        x:Class="HorosCloud.Desktop.Views.Previews.HeaderPreview"
        x:DataType="vm:HeaderPreviewViewModel"
        Width="1440" Height="56"
        Background="{DynamicResource BrushBackgroundBase}"
        Title="Preview: Header">
  <components:HorosHeaderBar DataContext="{Binding}" />
</Window>
```

## Design.PreviewWith (in Component)

```xml
<UserControl xmlns:previews="using:HorosCloud.Desktop.Views.Previews"
             ...>
  <Design.PreviewWith>
    <previews:HeaderPreview />
  </Design.PreviewWith>
  <!-- component markup -->
</UserControl>
```

## Preview ViewModel with Mock Data

```csharp
public partial class HeaderPreviewViewModel : ObservableObject
{
    public static HeaderPreviewViewModel DesignInstance { get; } = new()
    {
        AppTitle = "HorosCloud",
        UserName = "Alex M.",
        NotificationCount = 3
    };

    [ObservableProperty] private string _appTitle = "";
    [ObservableProperty] private string _userName = "";
    [ObservableProperty] private int _notificationCount;
}
```

## Never

- **Never** skip Preview because "the AXAML looks correct"
- **Never** test only inside full MainWindow during Pass 1
- **Never** proceed to Screenshot/Review without Preview running
- **Never** start the next region before current Preview is approved

